<paragraph id="IFRS03_42A"><paranum>42A</paranum><prolog><data name="standard_number" value="IFRS 3"/><data name="paranum" value="42A"/></prolog><body><variant base="F67034525" id="IFRS03_42A_V1">             <p id="IFRS03_P0167">When a <xref base="F16125609" href="../ifrs11/IFRS11_APPA.dita#IFRS11_APPA/IFRS11_P0087">party to a joint                         arrangement<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0284"/></ph></xref> (as defined in IFRS 11 <ph outputclass="standard_ref"><ph outputclass="standard_title">Joint Arrangements</ph></ph>) obtains <xref base="F16125786" href="../ifrs10/IFRS10_APPA.dita#IFRS10_APPA/IFRS10_P0160">control<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0053"/></ph></xref> of a <xref base="F4230839" href="IFRS03_APPA.dita#IFRS03_APPA/IFRS03_P0301">business<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0024"/></ph></xref> that is                 a <xref base="F16125586" href="../ifrs11/IFRS11_APPA.dita#IFRS11_APPA/IFRS11_P0082">joint operation<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0209"/></ph></xref> (as defined in IFRS 11), and had rights to the assets and                 obligations for the liabilities relating to that joint operation                  immediately before the <xref base="F4230836" href="IFRS03_APPA.dita#IFRS03_APPA/IFRS03_P0298">acquisition date<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0006"/></ph></xref>, the                 transaction is a <xref base="F4230842" href="IFRS03_APPA.dita#IFRS03_APPA/IFRS03_P0304">business combination<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0025"/></ph></xref> achieved                 in stages. The <xref base="F4230833" href="IFRS03_APPA.dita#IFRS03_APPA/IFRS03_P0297">acquirer<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0005"/></ph></xref> shall                 therefore apply the requirements for a business combination achieved in stages,                 including remeasuring its previously held interest in the joint operation in the                 manner described in <xref base="F68317746" href="IFRS03_42.dita#IFRS03_42/IFRS03_42_V2" id="IFRS03_X0249">paragraph 42</xref>. In doing so, the acquirer shall remeasure its entire                 previously held interest in the joint operation. </p>                      </variant></body></paragraph>